        "description": "Storyline\n\nIn the sprawling metropolis of Neo-Tokyo, the city is shrouded in darkness and neon lights. Crime lords and rogue AI have taken control, turning the once-thriving city into a dystopian nightmare. Amidst the chaos, you are a ninja warrior with a unique edge—armed with both a traditional katana and a high-tech gun. As the last guardian of the ancient ninja order, your mission is clear: defend the city from relentless assaults and restore order.\nKey Features\n\n1. Immersive VR Experience\n\n    Enter a fully immersive virtual reality world where you feel every swing of your katana and every shot from your gun. The high-fidelity graphics and realistic soundscapes make you feel like you’re truly in Neo-Tokyo.\n",
